    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_6_1607-1648",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1607-1648",
      "markText": "惟元无制度，其享国即在武力之上，其能箝制人民数十年而后动者，即其武力之横绝历代也。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1607&rangeEnd=1648",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1607&rangeEnd=1648"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_9_21239-21265",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "21239-21265",
      "markText": "其所可供后人议论者，正见明代士气之昌，非后来所能及尔",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=21239&rangeEnd=21265",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=21239&rangeEnd=21265"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_12_19325-19336",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "19325-19336",
      "markText": "明亡，时为清康熙三年。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=19325&rangeEnd=19336",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=19325&rangeEnd=19336"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_6_53960-54054",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "53960-54054",
      "markText": "至明之廷杖虽酷，然正人被杖，天下以为至荣，终身被人倾慕，此犹太祖以来，与臣下争意气不与臣下争是非所养成之美俗。清则君之处臣，必令天下颂为至圣，必令天下视被处者为至辱，此则气节之所以日卑也。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=53960&rangeEnd=54054",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=53960&rangeEnd=54054"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_8_31767-31805",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "31767-31805",
      "markText": "观于于谦终帝世不予雪，而害谦者则已次第戮之，故知非群小能害谦，自出英宗意尔。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=31767&rangeEnd=31805",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=31767&rangeEnd=31805"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_9_30468-30541",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "30468-30541",
      "markText": "李福达之狱，陛下驳勘再三，诚古帝王钦恤盛心，而诸臣负陛下，欺蔽者肆其谗，谄谀者溷其说，畏威者变其辞，访缉者淆其真。是以陛下惑滋甚，而是非卒不能明。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=30468&rangeEnd=30541",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=30468&rangeEnd=30541"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_7_20491-20524",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "20491-20524",
      "markText": "蹇义、夏原吉亦言不宜隳成功，而杨士奇、杨荣主罢兵息民，遂复安南国。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=20491&rangeEnd=20524",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=20491&rangeEnd=20524"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_8_3746-3772",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3746-3772",
      "markText": "敌国外患，反为廓清阉焰之一助，其后于明之全盛无损也。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3746&rangeEnd=3772",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3746&rangeEnd=3772"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_11_33445-33466",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "33445-33466",
      "markText": "卫所之军，亦为豪家供奔走，虽一诸生可役使之",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=33445&rangeEnd=33466",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=33445&rangeEnd=33466"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_6_42242-42333",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "42242-42333",
      "markText": "然以国家全体而论，当开创之后，而无检制元勋宿将之力，人人挟其马上之烈以自豪，权贵纵横，民生凋敝，其囯亦不可久也。功臣遭戮，千古叹汉、明两祖之少恩，其实亦汉、明开国之功，所以能速就耳。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=42242&rangeEnd=42333",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=42242&rangeEnd=42333"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_11_37755-37765",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "37755-37765",
      "markText": "举朝知其冤，莫敢言。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=37755&rangeEnd=37765",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=37755&rangeEnd=37765"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_7_18805-18848",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "18805-18848",
      "markText": "仁、宣两朝，蒙业而治，为明代极盛之时，承成祖之所得而其功未坠，沿成祖之所失而其弊亦未形",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=18805&rangeEnd=18848",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=18805&rangeEnd=18848"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_7_23729-23752",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "23729-23752",
      "markText": "，莫敢不服，以此德阉，一意重用，尽坏太祖成宪。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=23729&rangeEnd=23752",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=23729&rangeEnd=23752"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_8_15609-15618",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "15609-15618",
      "markText": "天位已定，宁复有他",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=15609&rangeEnd=15618",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=15609&rangeEnd=15618"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_10_12719-12802",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "12719-12802",
      "markText": "由雒于仁疏可见帝之昏惰。申时行遇事迁就，以成其过。留中之例开，言路无所施其匡救，于是庙堂争议，与君国不生效力，惟在臣僚间自为恩怨，朋党分歧，言论厖杂，任事者无所措手。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=12719&rangeEnd=12802",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=12719&rangeEnd=12802"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_12_3103-3126",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "3103-3126",
      "markText": "北兵至犹可议款，左逆至则若辈高官，我君臣死耳。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=3103&rangeEnd=3126",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=3103&rangeEnd=3126"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_6_37989-38017",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "37989-38017",
      "markText": "御史台古与省对立，明初改台为都察院，与部并立，是为七卿。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=37989&rangeEnd=38017",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=37989&rangeEnd=38017"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_6_3806-3826",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3806-3826",
      "markText": "是岁，巴延请杀张、王、刘、李、赵五姓汉人",
      "totalCount": 39,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=922804&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3806&rangeEnd=3826",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f6d326805e14b4f6d98ed9a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3806&rangeEnd=3826"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "922804_7_25703-25777",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "25703-25777",
      "markText": "其所以作此狡狯者，主者之意，必欲言帝王无野窜幸存之理，为绝天下系望崇祯太子之计，即太子复出，亦执定其为伪托，以处光棍之法处之也。此秉笔者之不得已也。",
